    <h2 class="mc mike-friends-blog"><strong>Mike &amp; Friends Blog</strong></h2>

    
      <div class="blogger">
        <a href="/blogger/peter-van-buren">
          <img class="blogshot" src="https://dwoq5s27enw2w.cloudfront.net/uploads/blogshots/peter-64x64.jpg"/>
          <p class="name">Peter Van Buren</p>
        </a>
        <p class="oneliner">Peter Van Buren is a State Department Foreign Service Officer who served in Iraq and author of &#39;We Meant Well: How I Helped Lose the Battle for the Hearts and Minds of the Iraqi People&#39;&#39;</p>
        <div class="clear"></div>
